metadata.name: Beauty #2
metadata.description: The Beauty Bunch is an exciting collection featuring 5,000 unique hockey players teaming up on the Ethereum blockchain as ERC-721A NFTs. Each Beauty is hand-drawn and randomized by software. All NFTs are 1/1 and generated from 400 possible traits. Our project is a members only access NFT community that is reimagining how hockey fans interact with their favorite pro players, teams and communities. Holders will experience exclusive access to athletes, games, memorabilia, events, partner giveaways & drops. The NFTs and The Beauty Bunch are not marketed, endorsed by or affiliated with the NHL, the NHLPA or any NHL team.
